         Saleem, I know the power of a 60 Shaman. See the thing is most shamans have zero clue as to how to PvP. 50% chance that if I meet a shaman he'll start trying to nuke me to death, like he's a goddam wizard or something. In any case, 60 shamans (esp. with torpor) are <i>extremely</i> rare. But you're right, a shaman is right up there in terms ov PvP. Personally, I'd rate a necro 3rd, maybe 2nd with some luck.</P><P><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>No channeling skill is a BITCH! Aint it :) Mahahahahahahaha!!<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote></P><P>lol amen</P><P>Cerilius brings up a very interesting point:<BR><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>Of course, most druids are idiots -- you could kill a hundred of them before you found one who knew what he was doing.<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote></P><P>Not only are most druids idiots, most people are idiots when it comes to PvP (Potus comes to mind, considering his pathetic strategies). But seriously, it continues to amaze me -- I play to PvP, and about 1 out of 8 people that I meet in PvP is actually smart and knows what they're doing. In other words, that one person has their own strategy and can counter my strategy fairly well.</P><P>Then there's those other 7 people. They believe that fighting people is just like fighting NPC's -- that every person is going to react the same way so there's only one strategy (wtg potus). For me, PvP is very strategic, and my strategies came from experience, that's why they work. But my point stands -- only 1 out of 8 people (approx) are actually a challange, the rest are so damn predictable I lose my interest in PvP.</P><P>Necro on Vallon Zek<BR>There is no cow level.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
