ees you, two can play that game.  With my epic I'm maxing around 44/hit currently.  Never know, you might get a lucky interrupt.</P><P>-Saleem<BR>Warlock of Xegony</P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
